**Technical:** N8N Pro license (if needed); LLM API credits (~$200-500); cloud computing; R/Python statistical software. **Human:** Supervisor (2h/week); peer reviewers (2-3); psychology domain expert; technical support. **Institutional:** Academic databases; computational resources; presentation opportunities; ethics board consultation.

